                    <description>&lt;p&gt;We should probably disable SSLv3.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/documentation/cve-2014-3566-2342133.html&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/documentation/cve-2014-3566-2342133.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
